title: in Appendix ―C‖
clause_text: in Appendix ―C‖. The qualification and procedure for registration and licensing of the Engineer / Structural Engineer / Town Planner / Supervisor shall be as given in Appendix-―C‖. An Architect registered with the Council of Architecture shall not be required to register with the Authority.
section: Qualification and Competence of the Architect / Licensed Engineer / Structural Engineer / Town Planner / Supervisor
